data.description: Come see this beautiful, recently remodeled home in Pacific, WA. This single level home is on a large fenced lot and features 3 bedrooms, 1 bathroom, wood-look flooring. Enter into small alcove then into the vaulted living room. The primary bedroom is also vaulted and has a slider door to a fully enclosed separate section of the back yard. Amazing kitchen with quartz counter-tops and all stainless steel appliances. All appliances stay including Washer & Dryer! Remodeled bath with oversized shower head. Very efficient use of space. Covered back deck with uncovered lower sun deck. Also a detached shop with bathroom, carport & additional finished building that could be used for an office, storage or art studio; also with separate deck. Nice!!!
